[Updated 29.04.2025]

 Cloudiboys All-in-One Nauvis LATE GAME Mall 

Hey there! 

I'm Cloudiboy, and today I want to share my Mall with you! 

 Whats inside?

This Mall includes everything you should produce ON NAUVIS LATE GAME 
a true all-in-one setup to keep your base supplied and running smoothly. 


 Highlights:

 The Mall features a light indicator system that shows you instantly:
 Whats being produced
 And where something might be missing!

 All inserters and chests are carefully configured, so nothing gets overproduced  no more mess or overflow! 

 The layout matches the in-game crafting menu, so you'll feel right at home and find everything quickly! 

 The entire system is mostly managed by logistic robots!

Only the few resource types that would overload the logistics network are fed in via belts 
everything else is handled cleanly by bots. 

 Hope you enjoy it!

I really hope you like my Mall 
and maybe a few of you will even have a little fun with it too! 

Best wishes,
Your Cloudiboy
